I think I have found the answer to my own question! The threads into the case
do not appear to be tapered and I found a German OP sender in my parts stash.
It threads into the hole with no wobble after the first thread is engaged into
the hole. So I am off to the flaps to see if I can find an aluminum crush ring
and a metric thread gauge. Hope it works!
